00:01:30.621 --> 00:01:33.887
Deepak Ramola: My mother
was only able to study until Class 5.

00:01:33.911 --> 00:01:37.447
Her grandmother did not want any girl
from the family to go to school.

00:01:37.471 --> 00:01:42.807
Mother often told us to study well,
since she never had the pleasure of books.

00:01:42.831 --> 00:01:44.567
One day, I got angry and told her

00:01:44.591 --> 00:01:47.127
she was lying about never
having been to school.

00:01:47.151 --> 00:01:50.532
Without understanding mathematics,
how do you manage household finances?

